42
00:05:08,290 --> 00:05:10,880
Hao Wei,

43
00:05:13,070 --> 00:05:16,150
viem, že si ku mne veľmi milý.

44
00:05:16,150 --> 00:05:18,020
Ale ja...

45
00:05:29,010 --> 00:05:30,670
Mi Mi,

46
